<item>
            <title>[LU-14270] enhance ha.sh to delay power up node</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14270</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In ClusterStor system a node in UNCLEAN state can be STONITHed after it has passed power down and power up already.&lt;br/&gt;
The patch adds ha_power_up_delay() in order to delay node&apos;s power up until CRM state became OFFLINE when failover pair is set and for $NODE_UP_DELAY seconds otherwise.&lt;br/&gt;
LOAD_TIMEOUT is added in order to ha_load_timeout be tunable.&lt;br/&gt;
The failover pair list for all victims are to be set via new -f option.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
